Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位選手都做好了準備
