Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人凝視
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提奧  借用一下你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破城錘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特選手將魔像擊得粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面  珂羅娜選手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出界倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.42,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(295,481)}珂羅娜·緹米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}20
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾威  珂羅娜小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}19
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵  還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}18
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}17
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量  體力  魔法量——在這些方面她是四人中最平凡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}16
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}15
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}14
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她能在危機時依然保持冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}13
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}12
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有為了獲勝而建立戰術的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的智慧和發散思維是四個人中最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那種狀態下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還握有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜選手  回到擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一回合還剩下20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓她在休息期間得到恢復的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後果無法設想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是珂羅娜同學並不會薇薇歐那樣的防守反擊以及格鬥戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣在近戰上壓倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為聖·希爾德的一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與薇薇歐相遇  成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她在練習格鬥技的時候大吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟她在一起於是與她一起練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道我是否真的喜歡格鬥技
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:06:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺如果放棄的話就沒法跟薇薇歐在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  我的訓練成績不像薇薇歐那樣好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法讓自己開心  有好幾次想要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個時候諾威師傅總會鼓勵我  指導我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著「最喜歡格鬥技了  想要變強」的薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠是那麼迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊說著「想更加熟練掌握春光拳」一邊努力的莉奧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承了先祖的遺志  想得到真正的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拚命著的愛因哈特是那麼出色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為在那隊伍中不拖後腿的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要繼續跟大家在同一高度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的速度前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜選手呆立原地  這會帶來危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算會疼痛  也要使用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強烈的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特選手  動彈不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}開始計時  1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(681,646)\fs36}Accel Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(890,646)\fs36}Revolver Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那不是薇薇歐的迅疾破碎和迴旋釘刺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(488,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳成功運作起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在此能決出勝負的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}6
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特選手能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}7
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}8
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來了  在計時至8的時候
