Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:18.40,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(1037,689)}損傷模擬  中度腦震盪  視野模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是雙方生命值已低至危險區域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場比賽勝負難料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:22.16,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(302,101)}珂羅娜·緹米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為她不會在格鬥戰中經行反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我低估了珂羅娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會就這樣結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩10秒…沒有時間創成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Wristlet Form
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護腕形態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(572,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用巨人之拳打倒她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽繼續進行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  珂羅娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候學會那種技術了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…在這裏決出勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:30.77,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(968,656)}損傷模擬  左臂劇烈扭傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強烈的打擊命中  但是第一回合已經結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特選手憑借微弱的生命值存活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜那招…是我的虎咆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(634,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然巨人之拳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體自動操作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  以操作魔像的方式來操作自己的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的力量足以操縱巨大的魔像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此進行打擊的話  就是名副其實的「巨人之拳」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時她應該是事前編好動作作為觸媒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得反擊動作能被自動觸發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  只要感應到特定打擊就自動作出反擊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就形成了無需反應時間的防守反擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對策呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才已經想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下個回合試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:43.80,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(269,479)}愛因哈特·斯崔特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:43.80,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(269,689)}損傷模擬  全身輕度扭傷  左臂中度扭傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳的運轉很穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個回合就以格鬥戰來決出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.02,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(1003,543)}珂羅娜·緹米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是珂羅娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那項技巧  格鬥戰也能贏對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回合  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(593,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳發動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(745,646)\fs36}Rush Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近距離格鬥速攻模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}System Load
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統讀取
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過上步發出猛烈連擊  這完全是薇薇歐同學的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Stun Knuckle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼拳擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(745,646)\fs36}Stun Knuckle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾威小姐的震撼拳擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反擊要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模式切換  完全防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:12:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春光拳的拆招動作  接下來是自動反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能夠預判了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是神速的自動反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會受到珂羅娜同學自身動作的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒法反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此  連擊的速攻也開始失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來  身體操作就會出現延遲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從判斷到動作的微妙延遲在格鬥戰中將是致命的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  如果是單發的大威力招式  就沒這個缺點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這樣  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(734,646)\fs36}Meist Arm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳  創成巨腕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體的自動操作和堅固的腕部武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說這個的對策是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從六百年前就一直在研究的課題了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:11.36,POS4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\bord0\pos(1000,670)}損傷模擬  右臂扭轉挫傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特選手  強烈的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  珂羅娜選手仍然堅挺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有進入擊倒倒計時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很痛  但應該還能繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(576,646)\fs36}Revolver Canon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(829,646)\fs36}Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是左手的迴旋炮擊然後是釘刺的連擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼體之型  牙山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不減弱威力  直接用肘部格擋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是利用對手的攻擊力的攻性防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:13:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜選手  用來攻擊的部位接連受到衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是愛因哈特選手的追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳頭要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  自動反擊還在運作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜選手倒地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}開始計時  1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確預判出自動反擊的發動時機  令其打空再加以反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且當勾拳完全展開後再從上方給予重擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}3
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  珂羅娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}4
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的攻性防禦讓拳和腿都受到了衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}5
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是信心受挫也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}6
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(515,646)\fs36}Meist Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(721,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為創成戰技和巨人之拳的精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才剛剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜選手站了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會就這麼結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(458,646)\fs36}Nephilim Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(732,646)\fs36}Full Control Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人之拳  五體完全操作模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五體的完全操作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是從外部進行驅動的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然感覺就原理跟提線木偶差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣的話也就能自由活動這隻手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這樣也沒問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  其實我很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜同學也到達了這一步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Phantom Dive
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈動潛擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被防住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  我也要不斷嘗試  直到打中為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是骨折  手臂撕裂卻仍然堅持戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是五體的完全外部操作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換的是超出極限的動作造成的身體損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生於和平時代的競技選手不應該使用這樣的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手和腳  還有全身都好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的王牌也無法達成決定性一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論我怎麼努力  都贏不了愛因哈特同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  信心受挫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒有發揮出練習時的全部實力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起練習時的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(617,646)\fs36}Golem Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為魔像創主的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄  讓我們見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有秘密的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不用這麼胡來的打法  珂羅娜小姐依然是很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你奧德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管我也是個格鬥技選手  但在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Tact Form
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動形態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動操作解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切換到魔法戰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提奧  全力警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Caging Spears
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁錮槍陣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(555,646)\fs36}Brunzell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  布倫希爾  再一次請求你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Yes anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(806,646)\fs36}Brunzell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以創主珂羅娜和魔導器布倫希爾之名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活吧  巨神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(714,646)\fs36}Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊碎她  歌利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(858,646)\fs36}Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用破城槌的話  一擊就能把歌利亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Maist Arm
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創成巨腕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Spiral Finger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋指擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習果然還是太辛苦了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是很奇怪自己為什麼要練到這個程度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這一切都是為了最美妙的瞬間而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最美妙的瞬間？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過練習  讓使出的招式變得利落時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重重地打出會心一擊時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切身體會到自己變得比之前更強大時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種瞬間  我希望你們能盡可能多的去體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有時也會讓你們練習得很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你也能體會到克服困難後所帶來的快樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Comet Blast
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗星衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾威師傅教給我的是成長所帶來的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我特訓的奧德對於我的成長由衷地感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要展示給他們看的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正能讓我感到自豪的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是我一個人冥思苦想出來的必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是整個團隊和教練一起為我打造的練習成果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Rock Bind
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅磐束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提奧  多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(744,646)\fs36}Brunzell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(911,646)\fs36}Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這一招決勝負吧  布倫希爾  歌利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Purge Blast
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射部件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Drill Crusher Punch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛鑽粉碎爆衝拳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王流  旋沖波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真正的最後一擊
